issues.description: One or more connections for profile "Profile_1" are configured with Use-BIOS boot settings. OneView does not support profile connections configured with a mixture of Use-BIOS and other boot settings.
issues.recommendation: The Virtual Connect Use-BIOS boot setting will be automatically changed to "not bootable" when the profile is migrated to OneView. If this change is acceptable, proceed with the migration.

issues.description: The WWNs for FC connection 1 of profile "Profile_1" will change to "user-specified" to maintain connectivity and retain the currently assigned WWNs.
issues.recommendation: If this change is acceptable, proceed with the migration.

issues.description: The WWNs for FC connection 2 of profile "Profile_1" will change to "user-specified" to maintain connectivity and retain the currently assigned WWNs.
issues.recommendation: If this change is acceptable, proceed with the migration.
